analyze

public java.util.List<Pair<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double>> analyze(EventSet unknown,
                                                                       java.util.List<EventSet> known)
Description copied from class: AnalysisDriver
Generic statistical analysis method. Analyze a given unknown EventSet in terms of its similarity (broadly defined) to elements of a List of EventSets of known authorship. Legacy code from WAY back. We should probably add a verify() method as well once the technology improves.

Overrides:
analyze in class AnalysisDriver
Parameters:
unknown - the EventSet to be analyzed
known - a vector of EventSets of known authorship
Returns:
a list of (name,numeric-result) pairs
